text.tspan: Filum is pretty cool. He's my best friend, and I've
known him almost as long as I've been alive. He does
this weird thing where he'll play the string instrument
on his face with two invisible hands that he has. Cool,
right? Also, today he wore a shirt that said "SPOOKI"
on it. I don't know why, and I've never seen him wear it
before. When I asked he said, "The fourth wall is made
to be broken." He's a bit crazy, but I still love him.
